        "important" : true,
        "name" : "Keep ROI if",
        "description" : "Filtering expression. This is applied per ROI. Click the 'f' button to see all available variables you can test for (note: requires from you to enable the corresponding measurement!).An example for an expression would be 'Area > 200 AND Mean > 10'.Annotations are available as variables."
