        "name" : "Operation",
        "description" : "The morphological operation. Following operations are supported: <ul><li><b>Erosion: </b>A local minimum filter</li><li><b>Dilation: </b>A local maximum filter</li><li><b>Opening: </b>Erosion, followed by dilation</li><li><b>Closing: </b>Dilation, followed by erosion</li><li><b>White Top Hat: </b>Image - Opening</li><li><b>Black Top Hat (Black Hat): </b>Closing - Image</li><li><b>Gradient: </b>Dilation - Erosion</li><li><b>Laplacian: </b>(Dilation + Erosion) / 2 - Image</li><li><b>Internal gradient: </b>Image - Erosion</li><li><b>External gradient: </b>Dilation - Image</li></ul>"
      },
