        "description" : "Allows to customize when two annotation sets are considered as equal. By default, non-empty annotation values should match exactly. You can also use a custom expression, instead."
      },
      "74e4db55-3bf1-40cc-ae0a-bf389a05a2fb/jipipe:parameter-slot-algorithm/parameter-annotations-prefix" : {
